==Dutch==

===Reflexive pronoun===
'''zich'''
# [[himself]], [[herself]], [[itself]], [[oneself]], [[themselves]]; (''polite form'') [[yourself]], [[yourselves]]
#: ''Hij wast zich.'' &mdash; He washes himself.
#: ''Hij wast zich het gezicht.'' &mdash; He washes his face.
#: ''Vergist u zich niet?'' &mdash; Aren't you mistaken? (''polite'')
#: ''Ik heb geen geld bij me.'' &mdash; I don't have any money on me.
#: ''Ieder voor zich.'' &mdash; Every man for himself.

